(DOOR OPENING)

593
01:05:18,081 --> 01:05:20,567
## (EERIE ORGAN)

594
01:05:20,667 --> 01:05:22,715
(FOOTSTEPS)

595
01:05:36,850 --> 01:05:39,319
(HYDRAULICS WHIRRING)

596
01:05:45,733 --> 01:05:47,861
(FOOTSTEPS CONTINUE)

597
