642
01:15:25,104 --> 01:15:27,357
(FAINT CHUCKLING)

643
01:15:31,861 --> 01:15:33,863
## (EERIE ORGAN)

644
01:16:11,150 --> 01:16:13,073
(FAINT CHUCKLING)

645
01:16:20,701 --> 01:16:22,920
(SCREAMING)

646
01:16:26,165 --> 01:16:29,009
(WIND GUSTING)

647
01:16:40,471 --> 01:16:42,565
Her car's still over there,

648
01:16:42,890 --> 01:16:46,019
and then there are footprints
leading up to here.

649
01:16:48,687 --> 01:16:50,815
## (EERIE ORGAN)

650
01:16:55,528 --> 01:16:57,781
And then nothing.

651
01:17:21,929 --> 01:17:23,706
(MOTOR WHIRRING)

652
01:17:23,806 --> 01:17:25,228
Okay!

653
01:17:25,558 --> 01:17:29,404
The Buick's right down there.
Bring it on up.

654
01:17:30,312 --> 01:17:32,781
(WHIRRING)

655
01:17:38,571 --> 01:17:41,916
